These are Puzzles for 4x5 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-4-1::.
There are 5 different favourite colors: lilac, lavender, blue, emerald, grey
The people have 5 different jobs:  analyst, bartender, firefighter, mechanic, project-manager
There 5 different types of food: cherry, apricot, papaya, kale, grapefruit
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: superhero, adventure, musical, disaster, action
 1. the person watching musical movies is on the left or right of the project-manager##3
 2. the analyst is in an odd position##4
 3. the person eating cherry is on the left of the person watching adventure movies##1
 4. the person who likes grey is on the right of the person eating kale##1
 5. the person who likes lilac is on the left or right of the analyst##3
 6. the person eating kale is on the right of the person who likes lilac##1
 7. the project-manager is on the right of the person eating papaya##1
 8. the person watching action movies is in an even position##4
 9. the person watching superhero movies is on the left or right of the mechanic##3
10. the person eating papaya is the firefighter##1
11. the person eating apricot is on the left of the person who likes lavender##1
12. the person who likes grey is on the left or right of the analyst##3
13. the person who likes grey is on the right of the person watching adventure movies##1
14. the person watching action movies is on the left of the person eating grapefruit##1
15. the person eating kale is the person who likes emerald##1
16. the person eating kale is on the right of the person who likes lilac##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |        2        |     3      |    4     |     5     |
| Color      | blue    | lilac   | emerald     | grey      | lavender      |
| Job           | firefighter | project-manager | analyst    | mechanic | bartender |
| Food   | papaya       | cherry         | kale      | apricot      | grapefruit    |
| Movie-Genre   | musical    | disaster         | adventure | action  | superhero   |

