.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-4-2::.
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: horror, time-travel, animation, adventure, scientific
There are 5 different nationalities: japanese, mexican, american, brazilian, colombian
City: london, paris, edinburgh, colone, san-francisco
The people use 5 different means of transport: boat, bus, quad-bike, roller, snowmobile
 1. the person watching animation movies is on the left or right of the person driving the roller##3
 2. the person watching scientific movies is on the right of the japanese##1
 3. the person watching animation movies is the colombian##1
 4. the person traveling to colone is on the left of the person watching time-travel movies##1
 5. the colombian is on the left of the person driving the snowmobile##1
 6. the american is in an odd position##4
 7. the person watching scientific movies is on the left or right of the person traveling to paris##3
 8. the person watching time-travel movies is between the person watching animation movies and the person driving the boat##2
 9. the person traveling to london is on the left or right of the mexican##3
10. the person traveling to london is on the left or right of the person watching horror movies##3
11. the person driving the roller is on the right of the person driving the boat##1
12. the person watching time-travel movies is on the left or right of the american##3
13. the person traveling to san-francisco is on the left or right of the person driving the quad-bike##3
14. the person traveling to san-francisco is on the left of the person watching animation movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |     3     |     4      |      5      |
| Movie-Genre         | adventure | time-travel | animation   | horror | scientific |
| Nationality   | american      | mexican   | colombian    | japanese        | brazilian        |
| City           | colone         | san-francisco  | london  | paris   | edinburgh      |
| Transport     | boat        | roller  | quad-bike | snowmobile | bus         |

