.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-4-3::.
There are 5 different favourite colors: mauve, yellow, turquise, pink, black
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: country, blues, salsa, ambient, jazz
House: gothic-revival, townhouse, craftsman, ranch-style, farmhouse
The people use 5 different means of transport: bike, scooter, skateboard, taxi, trike
 1. the person who likes yellow is on the left of the ranch-style house##1
 2. the gothic-revival house is on the left of the fan of ambient##1
 3. the fan of blues is on the right of the farmhouse house##1
 4. the person who likes pink is the person who likes pink##1
 5. the fan of jazz is on the right of the ranch-style house##1
 6. the fan of salsa is on the right of the fan of blues##1
 7. the craftsman house is on the far right##1
 8. the person driving the skateboard is on the left or right of the person driving the trike##3
 9. the fan of ambient is the person driving the skateboard##1
10. the person who likes mauve is the townhouse house##1
11. the person driving the taxi is the person who likes black##1
12. the townhouse house is between the person driving the scooter and the fan of country##2
13. the fan of country is on the left or right of the person who likes mauve##3
14. the farmhouse house is on the far left or far right##3
15. the person who likes black is in an odd position##4
16. the person who likes yellow is on the left or right of the person who likes pink##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |    3     |      4       |       5       |
| Color      | black       | mauve   | yellow    | pink     | turquise |
| Music-Genre   | country     | blues   | salsa   | ambient | jazz       |
| House         | farmhouse | townhouse | gothic-revival | ranch-style     | craftsman        |
| Transport     | taxi       | bike     | scooter  | skateboard   | trike         |

