.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-4-4::.
There are 5 different nationalities: argentine, chinese, french, thai, nigerian
The people have 5 different hobbies: singing, puzzles, dancing, photography, chess
5 different pets are kept: fish, snake, hedgehog, bird, rat
The people use 5 different means of transport: helicopter, quad-bike, ship, snowmobile, trike
 1. the person driving the quad-bike is between the person who's hobby is dancing and the person driving the helicopter##2
 2. the person who's hobby is photography is on the far right##1
 3. the thai is on the left of the chinese##1
 4. the person driving the helicopter is in an odd position##4
 5. the owner of the snake is on the left or right of the owner of the bird##3
 6. the person driving the trike is the argentine##1
 7. the person who's hobby is singing is on the right of the person driving the ship##1
 8. the owner of the hedgehog is on the left or right of the person driving the quad-bike##3
 9. the nigerian is the owner of the rat##1
10. the person who's hobby is puzzles is in an odd position##4
11. the owner of the bird is on the far left##1
12. the person driving the helicopter is on the far left or far right##3
13. the nigerian is on the right of the person who's hobby is singing##1
14. the argentine is the argentine##1
15. the person driving the snowmobile is the person who's hobby is chess##1
16. the french is on the right of the person who's hobby is dancing##1
17. the thai is on the left or right of the person driving the ship##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |   3    |     4      |     5      |
| Nationality          | argentine   | thai   | chinese | french       | nigerian       |
| Hobby   | puzzles | chess     | dancing   | singing     | photography    |
| Pet   | bird    | snake       | hedgehog    | fish | rat       |
| Transport     | trike    | snowmobile | ship   | quad-bike  | helicopter |

