11. the person driving the motorbike is the person watching scientific movies##1
12. the person driving the taxi is on the right of the person driving the snowmobile##1
13. the owner of the frog is the person who's hobby is hiking##1
14. the owner of the rat is on the right of the person driving the snowmobile##1
