The people use 5 different means of transport: trike, scooter, jet-ski, boat, bike
 1. the person drinking sprite is the person driving the boat##1
 2. the townhouse house is on the left or right of the gothic-revival house##3
 3. the townhouse house is on the left or right of the gothic-revival house##3
 4. the person drinking coffee is in an even position##4
 5. the person driving the trike is on the far left##1
 6. the owner of the chinchilla is between the person driving the bike and the owner of the mouse##2
 7. the person driving the jet-ski is between the person driving the boat and the owner of the goat##2
 8. the owner of the dog is the owner of the dog##1
 9. the person drinking cola is the person driving the trike##1
10. the person drinking lemonade is in the middle##1
11. the person drinking sprite is on the right of the art-deco house##1
12. the person driving the trike is on the left of the owner of the goat##1
13. the owner of the mouse is on the left or right of the owner of the cat##3
14. the palace house is on the right of the person driving the trike##1
15. the owner of the goat is on the right of the futuristic house##1
16. the gothic-revival house is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
