.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-4-8::.
The people have 5 different jobs:  designer, dressmaker, entrepreneur, librarian, musician
5 different games are played: bridge, domino, billiard, canasta, monopoly
There 5 different types of food: lettuce, grapes, blueberry, apple, cherry
There are 5 different favourite beverages: juice, water, almond-milk, sprite, fanta
 1. the person playing bridge is on the left or right of the person eating blueberry##3
 2. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left or right of the person eating lettuce##3
 3. the person drinking fanta is between the person drinking juice and the person eating apple##2
 4. the person drinking almond-milk is the person eating blueberry##1
 5. the entrepreneur is the person drinking juice##1
 6. the person drinking water is on the right of the librarian##1
 7. the designer is in the middle##1
 8. the person eating lettuce is on the left or right of the person playing monopoly##3
 9. the musician is in an even position##4
10. the person playing canasta is on the left of the person eating cherry##1
11. the person eating grapes is in an even position##4
12. the person playing billiard is on the left of the dressmaker##1
13. the musician is the person eating lettuce##1
14. the person playing monopoly is the person eating blueberry##1
15. the entrepreneur is on the right of the person eating grapes##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |    3     |     4      |      5       |
| Job           | librarian | musician   | designer | dressmaker | entrepreneur |
| Game   | monopoly    | bridge        | billiard   | canasta      | domino      |
| Food   | blueberry | lettuce    | apple   | grapes | cherry      |
| Beverage           | almond-milk       | water | sprite   | fanta     | juice         |

