.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-4-15::.
The people use 5 different means of transport: taxi, tram, quad-bike, trike, scooter
There are 5 different favourite beverages: 7up, fanta, cola, milk, hot-chocolate
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: cain, siglo, blend, havana, montecristo
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: baseball, basketball, cricket, sailing, skateboarding
 1. the person driving the tram is on the right of the cain-smoker##1
 2. the person drinking milk is on the left or right of the person who's sport is baseball##3
 3. the cain-smoker is on the left or right of the blend-smoker##3
 4. the blend-smoker is on the right of the person driving the taxi##1
 5. the person drinking milk is on the left of the blend-smoker##1
 6. the person who's sport is sailing is in an even position##4
 7. the person who's sport is baseball is on the left or right of the person drinking cola##3
 8. the siglo-smoker is between the person who's sport is cricket and the person driving the scooter##2
 9. the person drinking 7up is on the right of the person drinking fanta##1
10. the person drinking 7up is on the left or right of the blend-smoker##3
11. the person drinking 7up is in an odd position##4
12. the person who's sport is basketball is on the far right##1
13. the person driving the trike is on the far right##1
14. the person driving the scooter is on the far left or far right##3
15. the person who's sport is baseball is on the left or right of the montecristo-smoker##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2      |     3     |    4     |     5      |
| Transport          | scooter      | quad-bike       | taxi | tram | trike |
| Beverage   | cola       | hot-chocolate    | milk  | fanta  | 7up |
